<font size="20"><b>{\an8}<font face="Arial Black"><font size="35"><font color="#884a24">Usa<font color="#9e6629">neko Club</font></font></font></font></b></font>

4
00:00:09,780 --> 00:00:14,990
<font size="20"><b>{\an8}<font size="14">Produced by: <i>Usaneko</i> Anime Production Dept.</font></b></font>

5
00:00:15,760 --> 00:00:17,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kirara-san...</font>

6
00:00:18,050 --> 00:00:21,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>There's someone I've taken 
an interest in lately-usa.</i></font>

7
00:00:21,610 --> 00:00:25,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The more I try not to think about her, 
the more I think about her anyway.</i></font>

8
00:00:25,940 --> 00:00:30,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Because of that, I can no longer 
do things I used to be able to do.</i></font>

9
00:00:30,000 --> 00:00:32,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I feel like such an airhead.</i></font>

10
00:00:34,450 --> 00:00:39,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What is happening to me?</i></font>

11
00:00:40,910 --> 00:00:41,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">M...</font>

12
00:00:42,350 --> 00:00:43,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Memeru...</font>

13
00:00:44,640 --> 00:00:45,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So precious!</font>

14
00:00:45,980 --> 00:00:48,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It pains my heart!</font>

15
00:00:49,240 --> 00:00:51,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, Memeru.</font>

16
00:00:52,410 --> 00:00:54,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Precious girl...</font>

17
00:01:06,040 --> 00:01:08,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Another episode that soothes the soul.</font>

18
00:01:09,260 --> 00:01:12,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mimimi's smile was more 
mischievous than usual...</font>

19
00:01:16,760 --> 00:01:19,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Mimimi?!</font>

20
00:01:19,170 --> 00:01:21,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Usa-nya!</font>

21
00:01:22,310 --> 00:01:22,730
<font size="20"><b>{\an8}<font size="40"><font color="#f4be55">So?</font></font></b></font>

22
00:01:22,310 --> 00:01:22,730
<font size="20"><b>{\an8}<font size="40"><font color="#f4be55">So?</font></font></b></font>

23
00:01:22,730 --> 00:01:23,400
<font size="20"><b>{\an8}<font size="35"><font color="#f4be55">Who will you choose?</font></font></b></font>

24
00:01:22,730 --> 00:01:23,400
<font size="20"><b>{\an8}<font size="35"><font color="#f4be55">Who will you choose?</font></font></b></font>

