27
00:01:30,980 --> 00:01:31,140
<font size="28" color="#897b76"><b>{\an8}<font color="#ffffff">Pardon the Int<font color="#8dd4eb">rusion, I'm <font color="#ffffff">Home<i>!</i></font></font></font></b></font>

28
00:01:31,140 --> 00:01:36,410
<font size="28" color="#897b76"><b>{\an8}<font color="#ffffff">Pardon the Intrusion, I'm Home<i>!</i></font></b></font>

29
00:01:36,400 --> 00:01:36,700
<font size="20"><b>{\an8}<font size="12"><font color="#32605d">Rinko Nakama</font></font></b></font>

30
00:02:51,910 --> 00:02:55,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So anyway, this is my 
sister Mao. She's visiting.</font>

31
00:02:56,090 --> 00:02:57,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hmm...</font>

32
00:02:57,360 --> 00:02:59,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The more I look at her, the more 
I see the resemblance.</font>

33
00:03:00,660 --> 00:03:03,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, I did model Mimimi after her.</font>

34
00:03:03,140 --> 00:03:05,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Really? No wonder!</font>

35
00:03:06,450 --> 00:03:08,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh! It's <i>Magi Merm</i>!</font>

36
00:03:08,920 --> 00:03:13,300
<font size="20"><b>{\an8}<font face="Arial Black"><font size="25"><font color="#b94d9f">Magi<font color="#c866b1">c<font color="#cd8ab9">al <font color="#56b9da">Merm<font color="#92a9d0">a<font color="#a8abc8">id</font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></b></font>

37
00:03:08,920 --> 00:03:11,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whoa! You have the whole set!</font>

38
00:03:11,820 --> 00:03:14,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you like <i>Magi Merm</i>, too?</font>

39
00:03:14,550 --> 00:03:15,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah!</font>

40
00:03:15,500 --> 00:03:17,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I like the stuff that's on air now, too,</font>

41
00:03:17,480 --> 00:03:20,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but back when I watched the 
whole series on streaming,</font>

42
00:03:20,200 --> 00:03:22,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">my absolute faves were the Misaki sisters!</font>

43
00:03:22,480 --> 00:03:24,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Magi Merm</i> can really pull you in!</font>

44
00:03:24,930 --> 00:03:28,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Misaki sisters are super close, 
and their link outfits are so cute!</font>

45
00:03:28,780 --> 00:03:30,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And their magical pens match!</font>

46
00:03:30,820 --> 00:03:32,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Uh-huh!</font>

47
00:03:32,110 --> 00:03:34,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So does their Dream Color 
during their Jewelry Time!</font>

48
00:03:34,450 --> 00:03:37,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And also when the two of them 
combine their power for...</font>

49
00:03:37,080 --> 00:03:39,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Marble Star! Happy Happy Mode!</font>

50
00:03:39,770 --> 00:03:40,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I totally get you!</font>

51
00:03:40,930 --> 00:03:44,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not to mention their 
fairy-summoning smooth hair!</font>

52
00:03:44,540 --> 00:03:45,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whoosh!</font>

53
00:03:45,440 --> 00:03:46,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not following.</font>

54
00:03:46,850 --> 00:03:49,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Usa! Nya! Usa! Nya! Usa-usa—</i></font>

55
00:03:50,260 --> 00:03:51,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's up?</font>

56
00:03:52,230 --> 00:03:53,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Tada-Oja.</i></font>

57
00:03:52,960 --> 00:03:54,670
<font size="20"><b>{\an8}<font size="14"><font color="#f0fffd">Search</font></font></b></font>

58
00:03:54,670 --> 00:03:56,250
<font size="20"><b>{\an8}<font color="#6596ed">Making Big Robots! <font color="#371d24">Hug<font color="#6596ed">e Robot Technology</font></font></font></b></font>

59
00:03:55,890 --> 00:03:58,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hormones for relaxing.</font>

60
00:03:56,250 --> 00:03:58,630
<font size="20"><b>{\an8}<font color="#371d24">Hugs<font color="#6596ed"> Can Release Relaxation Hormones...</font></font></b></font>

61
00:03:56,250 --> 00:03:58,630
<font size="20"><b>{\an8}<font color="#6596ed">Great Effects! Stress Reduction Through Embraces...</font></b></font>

62
00:03:58,630 --> 00:04:04,220
<font size="20"><b>{\an8}<font color="#6596ed">The <font color="#371d24">Hug<font color="#6596ed"> Effect | <font color="#371d24">Hugs<font color="#6596ed"> can activate immune cells...</font></font></font></font></font></b></font>

63
00:03:58,860 --> 00:04:04,220
<font size="20"><b>{\an8}<font color="#6596ed">Don't be Fooled! A <font color="#371d24">Hug<font color="#6596ed">'s...</font></font></font></b></font>

64
00:03:58,900 --> 00:04:00,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stress reduction.</font>

65
00:04:00,700 --> 00:04:04,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Immune cells activate due 
to their healing effects.</font>

66
00:04:05,750 --> 00:04:07,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I guess that makes sense.</font>

67
00:04:09,610 --> 00:04:12,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Satsuki-san was tired then. 
That's why he...</font>

68
00:04:15,120 --> 00:04:16,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Relaxing...</font>

69
00:04:19,050 --> 00:04:20,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Healing effects...</font>

70
00:04:21,740 --> 00:04:24,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But I'm losing my mind from a hug!</i></font>

71
00:04:28,480 --> 00:04:32,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can neighbors affect it, too?</font>

72
00:04:33,750 --> 00:04:35,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Big Bro Haru!</font>

73
00:04:35,350 --> 00:04:36,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah?</font>

74
00:04:36,890 --> 00:04:39,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Big Sis Rinko's great, huh?</font>

75
00:04:39,520 --> 00:04:41,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Uh, sure.</font>

76
00:04:41,890 --> 00:04:44,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I mean, this is fifteen years old!</font>

77
00:04:44,680 --> 00:04:47,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can I really have it?</font>

78
00:04:47,810 --> 00:04:48,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Uh-huh.</font>

79
00:04:53,400 --> 00:04:55,650
<font size="20"><b>{\an8}<font face="Comic Sans MS"></font></b><font size="33"><font color="#848582"><s>Crush?</s></font></font></font>

80
00:04:59,960 --> 00:05:02,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll take good care of this!</font>

81
00:05:02,250 --> 00:05:06,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm glad I can pass it down to a new 
generation of <i>Magi Merm</i> fans.</font>

82
00:05:06,550 --> 00:05:10,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My classmates don't know older series,</font>

83
00:05:10,360 --> 00:05:14,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so I'm happy I got to talk to you about 
the greatness of the Misaki sisters!</font>

84
00:05:14,900 --> 00:05:16,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mao-chan...</font>

85
00:05:17,050 --> 00:05:18,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Big Sis...</font>

86
00:05:22,180 --> 00:05:24,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, get home safe.</font>

87
00:05:24,550 --> 00:05:25,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Uh-huh!</font>

88
00:05:25,500 --> 00:05:29,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Bye, Big Bro Haru, Big Sis!</font>

89
00:05:43,170 --> 00:05:47,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Usaharu-sensei, it's time for dinner.</font>

90
00:05:50,290 --> 00:05:51,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

91
00:05:52,140 --> 00:05:54,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh. I'll eat later.</font>

92
00:05:56,340 --> 00:05:58,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, okay...</font>

93
00:06:02,740 --> 00:06:06,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Usaharu-sensei's been acting weird lately.</i></font>

94
00:06:17,190 --> 00:06:18,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A crush?</font>

95
00:06:18,760 --> 00:06:20,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Yup!</i></font>

96
00:06:20,070 --> 00:06:23,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The Memeru episode that 
just aired was a huge hit!</i></font>

97
00:06:23,290 --> 00:06:25,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>So the crush arc in the manga 
the ep was based on</i></font>

98
00:06:25,400 --> 00:06:27,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>has been getting attention, too!</i></font>

99
00:06:27,530 --> 00:06:31,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, now that you mention it, readers kept 
mentioning it on the questionnaire, too.</font>

100
00:06:31,500 --> 00:06:36,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wanna read something that 
dives deeper into that plot!</font>

101
00:06:36,690 --> 00:06:38,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So let's write a continuation
 of that, Sensei!</font>

102
00:06:38,130 --> 00:06:39,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>So let's write a continuation
 of that, Sensei!</i></font>

103
00:06:39,370 --> 00:06:42,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's no continuation 
to that storyline.</font>

104
00:06:42,560 --> 00:06:44,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Besides, there's something else I wanna—</font>

105
00:06:44,330 --> 00:06:45,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What?!</i></font>

106
00:06:45,710 --> 00:06:47,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>You can't write it?!</i></font>

107
00:06:47,910 --> 00:06:48,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?!</font>

108
00:06:48,690 --> 00:06:50,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But you're a genius mangaka, right?!</i></font>

109
00:06:50,810 --> 00:06:52,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The acclaimed Usaharu-sensei won't do it?!</i></font>

110
00:06:52,770 --> 00:06:54,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>No way!</i></font>

111
00:06:54,410 --> 00:06:55,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait, hold up!</font>

112
00:06:55,530 --> 00:06:59,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I don't want to hear Usaharu-sensei 
say stuff like tha—</i></font>

113
00:06:56,520 --> 00:06:58,480
<font size="20"><b>{\an8}Editor Kaneko</b></font>

114
00:07:00,050 --> 00:07:01,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I just...</font>

115
00:07:08,240 --> 00:07:11,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">don't know anything 
about having a crush.</font>

116
00:07:12,540 --> 00:07:15,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Could this be...</i></font>

117
00:07:16,170 --> 00:07:17,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>love?!</i></font>

118
00:07:17,900 --> 00:07:19,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Tada-Oja!</i></font>

119
00:07:19,830 --> 00:07:22,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A crush, you say?</font>

120
00:07:25,590 --> 00:07:28,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Frankly, I don't have a clue 
what the big deal is.</font>

121
00:07:28,550 --> 00:07:31,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've never had a crush on anyone before.</font>

122
00:07:32,970 --> 00:07:35,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Having a crush is just 
a huge inconvenience!</font>

123
00:07:36,350 --> 00:07:38,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My assistants have gotten
 into fights over me before.</font>

124
00:07:38,920 --> 00:07:42,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We couldn't finish 
our work because of it.</font>

125
00:07:42,570 --> 00:07:45,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yikes... That's one heck of a backstory.</font>

126
00:07:46,490 --> 00:07:48,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I only hired you 'cause 
you're already taken.</font>

127
00:07:50,940 --> 00:07:52,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm sorry it's all fake.</i></font>

128
00:07:52,990 --> 00:07:55,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">People with crushes need to 
stop beating around the bush</font>

129
00:07:55,670 --> 00:07:57,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and just ask them out already!</font>

130
00:07:57,250 --> 00:07:59,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you get dumped, move on!</font>

131
00:08:00,610 --> 00:08:02,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But...</font>

132
00:08:02,960 --> 00:08:06,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't think Memeru is that kind of girl.</font>

133
00:08:06,770 --> 00:08:08,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know that!</font>

134
00:08:08,650 --> 00:08:09,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're absolutely right!</font>

135
00:08:09,750 --> 00:08:11,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Tada-Oja!</i></font>

136
00:08:11,760 --> 00:08:14,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Usaharu-sensei is in full-focus 
mode again tonight,</font>

137
00:08:14,790 --> 00:08:16,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so I came over here.</font>

138
00:08:17,290 --> 00:08:19,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're more than welcome here.</font>

139
00:08:19,140 --> 00:08:20,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're my girlfriend, after all.</font>

140
00:08:21,250 --> 00:08:22,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sure...</font>

141
00:08:43,320 --> 00:08:46,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Writer's block isn't that rare.</font>

142
00:08:48,320 --> 00:08:50,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Writers and artists 
aren't gods, after all.</font>

143
00:08:56,160 --> 00:08:57,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lunch is ready!</font>

144
00:09:00,580 --> 00:09:02,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Leave it there.</font>

145
00:09:05,930 --> 00:09:07,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Would you like to eat together?</font>

146
00:09:18,400 --> 00:09:21,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You should eat, even just a little...</font>

147
00:09:21,580 --> 00:09:22,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shut up!</font>

148
00:09:22,710 --> 00:09:24,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's your deal?!</font>

149
00:09:24,710 --> 00:09:27,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you my editor?! My mom?!</font>

150
00:09:27,040 --> 00:09:29,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Or my girlfriend or something?!</font>

151
00:09:30,340 --> 00:09:31,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm your disciple!</font>

152
00:09:32,700 --> 00:09:34,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm also your chef-sistant!</font>

153
00:09:34,600 --> 00:09:37,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's my duty to make sure you eat!</font>

154
00:09:37,350 --> 00:09:41,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll say whatever I have to so that you
 can be healthy and write your manga!</font>

155
00:09:44,290 --> 00:09:46,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not hungry.</font>

156
00:09:46,480 --> 00:09:47,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then sleep!</font>

157
00:09:47,950 --> 00:09:49,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not tired!</font>

158
00:09:50,760 --> 00:09:52,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then go take a bath!</font>

159
00:09:52,220 --> 00:09:53,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Tada-Oja!</i></font>

160
00:10:01,410 --> 00:10:03,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is it too hot?</font>

161
00:10:05,250 --> 00:10:06,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Feels good.</font>

162
00:10:07,810 --> 00:10:11,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I think he's calmed down a little.</i></font>

163
00:10:11,620 --> 00:10:14,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I want Usaharu-sensei to go 
back to his energetic self.</i></font>

164
00:10:15,730 --> 00:10:18,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But what can I possibly do?</i></font>

165
00:10:29,830 --> 00:10:32,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's with you all of a sudden?</font>

166
00:10:33,810 --> 00:10:37,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hugs are good when you're tired.</font>

167
00:10:37,410 --> 00:10:40,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Isn't that more for couples?</font>

168
00:10:41,170 --> 00:10:44,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Y-You're right.</font>

169
00:10:46,030 --> 00:10:49,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? Do you like me or something?</font>

170
00:10:50,300 --> 00:10:51,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I love you very much!</font>

171
00:10:53,790 --> 00:10:56,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's a problem when my 
assistants fall for me, though.</font>

172
00:10:56,300 --> 00:10:57,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As your faithful follower!</font>

173
00:10:59,300 --> 00:11:02,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you for bringing 
<i>Usaneko Club</i> to life!</font>

174
00:11:02,790 --> 00:11:05,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll forever be grateful!</font>

175
00:11:05,930 --> 00:11:08,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>These are some wild pick-up lines.</i></font>

176
00:11:09,440 --> 00:11:12,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Rinko, maybe you...</font>

177
00:11:12,690 --> 00:11:15,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">like me more than that guy?</font>

178
00:11:15,940 --> 00:11:16,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

179
00:11:18,370 --> 00:11:20,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Absolutely not.</font>

180
00:11:20,450 --> 00:11:21,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Satsuki-san!</font>

181
00:11:22,640 --> 00:11:24,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nakama-san...</font>

182
00:11:24,130 --> 00:11:26,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What exactly are you doing?</font>

183
00:11:26,580 --> 00:11:29,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yo. Your girlfriend's cheating on you.</font>

184
00:11:29,760 --> 00:11:31,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ch-Cheating?</font>

185
00:11:33,210 --> 00:11:36,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm s-s-sorry!</font>

186
00:11:36,970 --> 00:11:40,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wasn't cheating or anything!</font>

187
00:11:40,360 --> 00:11:41,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Calm down.</font>

188
00:11:41,720 --> 00:11:45,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know I'm the one you really love.</font>

189
00:11:45,720 --> 00:11:47,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um...</font>

190
00:11:47,560 --> 00:11:48,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I...</font>

191
00:11:52,690 --> 00:11:53,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I...</font>

192
00:11:55,640 --> 00:11:57,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I...</font>

193
00:11:59,030 --> 00:12:02,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry. I know you have trouble 
saying it in front of others.</font>

194
00:12:04,340 --> 00:12:07,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then you can just nod for me.</font>

195
00:12:08,750 --> 00:12:12,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm the only one you love, right?</font>

196
00:12:13,630 --> 00:12:16,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Satsuki-san is too amazing.</i></font>

197
00:12:16,510 --> 00:12:18,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He gives off such boyfriend energy!</i></font>

198
00:12:23,870 --> 00:12:25,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good job.</font>

199
00:12:26,100 --> 00:12:28,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Whoa! Satsuki-san!</i></font>

200
00:12:28,700 --> 00:12:32,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>H-He's being such an exemplary boyfriend!</i></font>

201
00:12:32,390 --> 00:12:34,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What am I being forced to watch?</font>

202
00:12:35,700 --> 00:12:39,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As you can see, Nakama-san 
is obsessed with me.</font>

203
00:12:39,030 --> 00:12:41,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">E-Eep...</font>

204
00:12:41,040 --> 00:12:42,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tch.</font>

205
00:12:42,280 --> 00:12:45,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why'd she hug me, then?</font>

206
00:12:45,690 --> 00:12:48,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sure she simply wanted 
to relieve your stress.</font>

207
00:12:48,130 --> 00:12:50,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Exactly! I had no ulterior 
motives whatsoever!</font>

208
00:12:50,790 --> 00:12:55,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was just wondering how I could help 
you with your manuscript writing!</font>

209
00:12:56,000 --> 00:12:58,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, whatever.</font>

210
00:12:58,830 --> 00:13:02,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just don't come to me crying 
"we broke up becuse of you" later.</font>

211
00:13:02,800 --> 00:13:04,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It'd leave a bad aftertaste.</font>

212
00:13:04,930 --> 00:13:07,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't worry. We love each other.</font>

213
00:13:08,730 --> 00:13:09,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Anyway...</font>

214
00:13:11,990 --> 00:13:15,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How's your progress going, 
Mr. Writer's Block?</font>

215
00:13:16,300 --> 00:13:17,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What was that?</font>

216
00:13:17,810 --> 00:13:19,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's take this outside!</font>

217
00:13:19,300 --> 00:13:20,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">S-Sensei!</font>

218
00:13:20,600 --> 00:13:22,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fine. Let's go.</font>

219
00:13:22,330 --> 00:13:23,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

220
00:13:23,330 --> 00:13:24,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Eh?</font>

221
00:13:26,530 --> 00:13:30,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What you need now is a walk.</font>

222
00:13:30,620 --> 00:13:34,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's not good for you to stay inside
 hunched over your desk.</font>

223
00:13:35,250 --> 00:13:38,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Instead of toiling away 
with your brain, walk.</font>

224
00:13:38,100 --> 00:13:40,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Unravel the stressors 
in your brain by walking.</font>

225
00:13:40,970 --> 00:13:43,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You didn't know this even as a creator?</font>

226
00:13:46,430 --> 00:13:49,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Take a moment to put aside 
any work that involves thinking.</font>

227
00:13:50,760 --> 00:13:54,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see! So you need to enjoy a walk?</font>

228
00:13:54,110 --> 00:13:56,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can help with that—</font>

229
00:13:58,860 --> 00:14:02,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nakama-san and I are 
only here to chaperone.</font>

230
00:14:11,050 --> 00:14:11,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tsk.</font>

231
00:14:11,910 --> 00:14:15,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's so friggin' bright and too damn cold.</font>

232
00:14:16,210 --> 00:14:19,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Also, I don't have writer's block.</i></font>

233
00:14:19,300 --> 00:14:23,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I can write whatever I want at any time.</i></font>

234
00:14:23,600 --> 00:14:24,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Damn it.</i></font>

235
00:14:24,590 --> 00:14:26,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What's the big deal with crushes?</i></font>

236
00:14:29,310 --> 00:14:30,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm freezing.</font>

237
00:14:30,970 --> 00:14:32,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The slide! The slide!</font>

238
00:14:32,810 --> 00:14:35,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did you know I can go down the slide?</font>

239
00:14:35,000 --> 00:14:36,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow, that's amazing!</font>

240
00:14:36,690 --> 00:14:40,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}I'm not scared of slides!</font>

241
00:14:37,530 --> 00:14:40,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>When did the wind get so cold?</i></font>

242
00:14:40,510 --> 00:14:42,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, no running!</font>

243
00:14:45,450 --> 00:14:46,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There, there.</font>

244
00:14:46,830 --> 00:14:48,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That was scary, huh?</font>

245
00:14:48,490 --> 00:14:51,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not... scared of the slide.</font>

246
00:14:51,140 --> 00:14:53,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aw. So close.</font>

247
00:14:51,470 --> 00:14:54,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's go to the slide sometime, okay?</font>

248
00:14:59,650 --> 00:15:01,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Well, I guess...</i></font>

249
00:15:01,890 --> 00:15:04,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I can feel my brain unwinding.</i></font>

250
00:15:08,890 --> 00:15:11,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But y'know, Memeru...</i></font>

251
00:15:12,290 --> 00:15:15,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I still don't get how you feel.</i></font>

252
00:15:16,100 --> 00:15:19,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Belonging to someone else sounds
 like the most annoying crap ever.</i></font>

253
00:15:19,850 --> 00:15:21,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why bother falling for someone?</font>

254
00:15:21,690 --> 00:15:23,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Usaharu-sensei!</font>

255
00:15:28,050 --> 00:15:29,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here!</font>

256
00:15:28,620 --> 00:15:29,990
<font size="20"><b>{\an8}<font size="11"><font color="#bd6127">Corn Potage</font></font></b></font>

257
00:15:30,670 --> 00:15:31,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks.</font>

258
00:15:40,130 --> 00:15:43,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sensei, do you remember episode 43?</font>

259
00:15:49,010 --> 00:15:51,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I guess there was 
an episode like that.</font>

260
00:15:51,130 --> 00:15:55,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sukoko won a whole bunch for 
free from a vending machine!</font>

261
00:15:55,260 --> 00:16:01,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She was so cute trying to get the last 
corn kernel from her hundredth can!</font>

262
00:16:02,370 --> 00:16:04,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, yeah.</font>

263
00:16:11,010 --> 00:16:11,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ah!</font>

264
00:16:11,740 --> 00:16:14,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This ginkgo leaf reminds me 
of Mimimi from episode 112!</font>

265
00:16:14,790 --> 00:16:17,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They drew everyone's faces 
on gingko leaves.</font>

266
00:16:18,170 --> 00:16:22,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And when Mimimi saw it, she said, 
"That's not what my face looks like!"</font>

267
00:16:20,980 --> 00:16:23,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}She's so damn cute.</i></font>

268
00:16:22,220 --> 00:16:24,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and threw a fit.</font>

269
00:16:26,530 --> 00:16:27,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Rin—</font>

270
00:16:27,050 --> 00:16:27,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nakama-san!</font>

271
00:16:28,610 --> 00:16:32,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry! I disturbed you when 
you shouldn't be thinking at all!</font>

272
00:16:32,080 --> 00:16:33,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll take my leave!</font>

273
00:16:38,610 --> 00:16:41,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Based on my whole life experience,</i></font>

274
00:16:44,560 --> 00:16:49,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>the reason Rinko looks so cute...</i></font>

275
00:16:50,580 --> 00:16:53,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>is probably because 
she likes me after all.</i></font>

276
00:16:53,380 --> 00:16:56,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Girls get cuter when they're 
near the person they like.</i></font>

277
00:16:57,320 --> 00:17:01,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Well, in Rinko's case, it's probably 
my manga that she's in love with.</i></font>

278
00:17:01,960 --> 00:17:04,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But same difference, right?</i></font>

279
00:17:04,410 --> 00:17:07,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>If she likes my manga, then she likes me.</i></font>

280
00:17:07,180 --> 00:17:07,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Am I wrong?</i></font>

281
00:17:10,340 --> 00:17:13,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who makes a face like that at 
someone they're not in love with?</font>

282
00:17:14,670 --> 00:17:17,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Okay. One more time.</i></font>

283
00:17:17,100 --> 00:17:22,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>If Rinko catches me looking at her, then 
turns around and smiles one more time...</i></font>

284
00:17:22,810 --> 00:17:27,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It proves that she's 
totally in love with me.</i></font>

285
00:17:27,500 --> 00:17:29,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>One more time...</i></font>

286
00:17:30,940 --> 00:17:33,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>If she turns around one more time...</i></font>

287
00:17:39,970 --> 00:17:43,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Why isn't she turning around?! 
Even after being all suggestive?!</i></font>

288
00:17:43,450 --> 00:17:44,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What's with her?</i></font>

289
00:17:44,820 --> 00:17:46,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Read the room!</i></font>

290
00:17:46,250 --> 00:17:48,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>You're making me feel this way...</i></font>

291
00:17:50,040 --> 00:17:52,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Feel this way?</font>

292
00:17:54,140 --> 00:17:56,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Feel this way?!</i></font>

293
00:18:04,640 --> 00:18:06,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So this is it?</font>

294
00:18:06,030 --> 00:18:07,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see...</font>

295
00:18:08,270 --> 00:18:10,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can totally write this stuff.</font>

296
00:18:10,800 --> 00:18:12,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Usaharu-sensei!</font>

297
00:18:12,120 --> 00:18:13,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's wrong?!</font>

298
00:18:13,400 --> 00:18:14,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you feel sick?!</font>

299
00:18:15,620 --> 00:18:16,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The...</font>

300
00:18:17,360 --> 00:18:18,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"The"?</font>

301
00:18:18,410 --> 00:18:19,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The baby's coming...</font>

302
00:18:19,660 --> 00:18:21,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you in labor?!</font>

303
00:18:21,550 --> 00:18:24,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shit, the head's already out...</font>

304
00:18:25,010 --> 00:18:27,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A-Are you giving birth to a story?</font>

305
00:18:27,560 --> 00:18:30,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Memeru coincidentally shows up there...</font>

306
00:18:30,090 --> 00:18:32,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And then Kirara...</font>

307
00:18:32,050 --> 00:18:34,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But Kirara doesn't notice...</font>

308
00:18:35,420 --> 00:18:36,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There!</font>

309
00:18:38,210 --> 00:18:39,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's coming...</font>

310
00:18:39,780 --> 00:18:41,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please hold on a little longer!</font>

311
00:18:47,790 --> 00:18:49,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This...</i></font>

312
00:18:49,840 --> 00:18:51,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This is...</i></font>

313
00:18:51,820 --> 00:18:53,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This is...</i></font>

314
00:18:55,340 --> 00:18:57,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This is what having a crush is!</i></font>

315
00:18:57,570 --> 00:18:58,830
<font size="20"><b>{\an8}<font face="Comic Sans MS"><font color="#8f6c57">That's why I can't
 forget you!</font></font></b></font>

316
00:18:59,210 --> 00:19:01,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Right, Memeru?!</i></font>

317
00:19:09,250 --> 00:19:10,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's done.</font>

318
00:19:11,120 --> 00:19:13,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Already?!</font>

319
00:19:13,340 --> 00:19:14,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're amazing!</font>

320
00:19:16,850 --> 00:19:18,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's no sweat.</font>

321
00:19:18,860 --> 00:19:21,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Congratulations on your birth!</font>

322
00:19:21,050 --> 00:19:23,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You worked so hard!</font>

323
00:19:23,100 --> 00:19:25,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Looks like you got something 
out thanks to the walk.</font>

324
00:19:25,600 --> 00:19:26,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

325
00:19:26,520 --> 00:19:28,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's because I'm a genius, duh!</font>

326
00:19:28,350 --> 00:19:30,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You really are amazing!</font>

327
00:19:30,140 --> 00:19:32,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We were taking the same paths, 
drinking the same drinks...</font>

328
00:19:32,860 --> 00:19:35,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But you were able to give 
birth to a whole story!</font>

329
00:19:35,740 --> 00:19:38,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You really are a god, Usaharu-sensei!</font>

330
00:19:39,100 --> 00:19:40,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You could say that.</font>

331
00:19:42,920 --> 00:19:47,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your "god" wasn't even able to eat 
a decent meal until a while ago.</font>

332
00:19:50,020 --> 00:19:52,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wanna go home and eat Rinko's cooking.</font>

333
00:19:52,090 --> 00:19:53,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">O-Of course!</font>

334
00:19:54,270 --> 00:19:56,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's have something warm!</font>

335
00:20:00,640 --> 00:20:06,020
<font size="20"><b>{\an8}<font face="Verdana"><font size="9"><font color="#d3ae5e">Always by your side
Seven Mart</font></font></font></b></font>

336
00:20:01,970 --> 00:20:04,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll go handle the grocery shopping first!</font>

337
00:20:04,590 --> 00:20:06,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll go with you.</font>

338
00:20:06,020 --> 00:20:09,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is my job as the chef-sistant, 
so please wait here.</font>

339
00:20:13,230 --> 00:20:14,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Tada-Oja.</i></font>

340
00:20:17,310 --> 00:20:20,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So how long have you two been together?</font>

341
00:20:21,370 --> 00:20:24,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Frankly, you don't seem that close. 
You're not even on a first-name basis.</font>

342
00:20:25,140 --> 00:20:27,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So how'd you start dating? Who asked who?</font>

343
00:20:27,780 --> 00:20:28,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Usada.</font>

344
00:20:29,620 --> 00:20:31,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Didn't you say having
 a crush is inconvenient?</font>

345
00:20:31,830 --> 00:20:33,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't try unless you're serious.</font>

346
00:20:34,180 --> 00:20:37,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I only wanted to chat 
about your love life.</font>

347
00:20:37,010 --> 00:20:38,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So? How's it going?</font>

348
00:20:38,930 --> 00:20:40,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You guys do it yet?</font>

349
00:20:40,370 --> 00:20:41,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Usada!</font>

350
00:20:44,180 --> 00:20:48,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For a glasses-type character, 
you've got quite a violent streak.</font>

351
00:20:48,530 --> 00:20:50,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Am I right, Satsukiller-sensei?</font>

352
00:20:55,070 --> 00:20:59,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know I said not to break up 
because of me, but I take it back.</font>

353
00:20:59,710 --> 00:21:00,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Forget I said it.</font>

